headline.print_headline: Indian PM Modi's Party Unlikely to Form Jammu & Kashmir Government: Polls
headline.main: Indian PM Modi's Party Unlikely to Form Jammu & Kashmir Government: Polls

lead_paragraph: Indian Prime Minister Narendra Modi's party will not win enough seats to form a government in Jammu and Kashmir state, two exit polls showed on Saturday, dampening its hopes of taking control of the state for the first time.
